    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 9th level, Battle Song Enhancement</em></p>\n<p>While playing your Song of Battle, when you cast a tech power or use a class feature that affects other creatures within the radius of your song, you can choose a number of them equal to 1 + the power's level. The chosen creatures automatically succeed on their saving throws against the power, and they take no damage if they would normally take half damage on a successful save.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you use your Battle Song Enhancement feature, you create a third burst.</p>",
